OL,3,CCalls to legally require supermarkets
OL,4,Cto reveal 'shrinkflation' to customers
OL,6,FSupermarkets would be forced to tell
OL,7,Ftheir customers if they want them to
OL,8,F"pay more for less" under proposals
OL,9,Fdesigned to tackle "shrinkflation".
OL,11,FThe Liberal Democrats want government
OL,12,Flegislation amended to legally require
OL,13,Flarge supermarkets to inform shoppers
OL,14,Fwhen the quantity of goods within a
OL,15,Fpre-packaged product has decreased
OL,16,Fthereby increasing the price per unit
OL,17,Fof measurement.
