OL,3,CCalls to legally require supermarkets
OL,4,Cto reveal 'shrinkflation' to customers
OL,6,FDetails of the changes would need to
OL,7,Fbe attached or placed alongside the
OL,8,Fproduct for a 60-day period, according
OL,9,Fto the amendment tabled to the Product
OL,10,FRegulation and Metrology Bill.
OL,12,FDigestive biscuits, butter, crisps and
OL,13,Fchocolate bars were among the items
OL,14,Ffound to have decreased in size while
OL,15,Ftheir unit cost increased, according
OL,16,Fto 2024 research by Compare the Market.
OL,18,FMPs could be asked to vote on the Lib
OL,19,FDem proposal on Wednesday when the
OL,20,FBill returns to the Commons for its
OL,21,Freport stage.
