OL,3,CCalls to legally require supermarkets
OL,4,Cto reveal 'shrinkflation' to customers
OL,6,FLib Dem trade spokesman Clive Jones
OL,7,Fsaid: "The scourge of shrinkflation
OL,8,Fneeds to be exposed.
OL,10,F"Shoppers have been hammered during a
OL,11,Fcost-of-living crisis all while
OL,12,Fmassive companies and big supermarket
OL,13,Fchains are forcing them to pay more
OL,14,Ffor less to protect their bottom lines.
OL,16,F"They need to be called out on it and
OL,17,Ffor shoppers to know when they are at
OL,18,Frisk of being ripped off.
