OL,3,CCalls to legally require supermarkets
OL,4,Cto reveal 'shrinkflation' to customers
OL,6,F"The Government should accept this
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat amendment so that we
OL,8,Fcan help protect shoppers and their
OL,9,Falready stretched household budgets
OL,10,Ffrom another round of shrinkflation."
OL,12,FThe Bill as a whole gives powers to
OL,13,Fministers to regulate the marketing
OL,14,Fand use of goods in the UK after
OL,15,FBrexit.
OL,17,FIt was previously amended in the House
OL,18,Fof Lords to provide protections to the
OL,19,Fimperial pint measure to ease fears
OL,20,Fover its future.
