OL,6,FThe changes accepted by the Government
OL,7,Fwould bar ministers from preventing or
OL,8,Frestricting the use of the pint in
OL,9,Frelation to draught beer, cider or
OL,10,Fmilk in returnable containers.
OL,12,FIt also provides a definition of a
OL,13,Fpint as 0.56826125 cubic decimetres.
OL,15,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,16,Fspokesman said: "We're committed to
OL,17,Fprotecting consumers from unfair
OL,18,Fcommercial practices and making sure
OL,19,Fthey have all the information they
OL,20,Fneed to make informed decisions on
OL,21,Fpurchases.
